{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":785,"text":"So on my way here,"},{"time":3840,"text":"the passenger next to me and I\nhad a very interesting conversation"},{"time":7542,"text":"during my flight."},{"time":9585,"text":"He told me, \"It seems like\nthe United States has run out of jobs,"},{"time":14113,"text":"because they're just making some up:"},{"time":16481,"text":"cat psychologist, dog whisperer,\ntornado chaser.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":22743,"text":"A couple of seconds later, he asked me,"},{"time":25560,"text":"\"So what do you do?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":27812,"text":"And I was like, \"Peacebuilder?\""},{"time":30505,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":34925,"text":"Every day, I work to amplify\nthe voices of women"},{"time":39352,"text":"and to highlight their experiences"},{"time":42450,"text":"and their participation in peace\nprocesses and conflict resolution,"},{"time":47509,"text":"and because of my work,"},{"time":50288,"text":"I recognize that the only way to ensure\nthe full participation of women globally"},{"time":56464,"text":"is by reclaiming religion."}]},{"cues":[{"time":59330,"text":"Now, this matter is vitally\nimportant to me."},{"time":63394,"text":"As a young Muslim woman,\nI am very proud of my faith."},{"time":67805,"text":"It gives me the strength and conviction\nto do my work every day."},{"time":72540,"text":"It's the reason I can be here\nin front of you."},{"time":75909,"text":"But I can't overlook the damage that has\nbeen done in the name of religion,"},{"time":81133,"text":"not just my own, but all\nof the world's major faiths."},{"time":85661,"text":"The misrepresentation and misuse\nand manipulation of religious scripture"},{"time":90165,"text":"has influenced our social\nand cultural norms,"},{"time":93694,"text":"our laws, our daily lives,"},{"time":96620,"text":"to a point where we sometimes\ndon't recognize it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100804,"text":"My parents moved from Libya,\nNorth Africa, to Canada"},{"time":105490,"text":"in the early 1980s,"},{"time":107254,"text":"and I am the middle child of 11 children."},{"time":111100,"text":"Yes, 11."},{"time":113431,"text":"But growing up, I saw my parents,"},{"time":115589,"text":"both religiously devout\nand spiritual people,"},{"time":119165,"text":"pray and praise God for their blessings,"},{"time":121905,"text":"namely me of course, but among others.\n(Laughter)"},{"time":126664,"text":"They were kind and funny and patient,"},{"time":129822,"text":"limitlessly patient, the kind of patience\nthat having 11 kids forces you to have."},{"time":136161,"text":"And they were fair."},{"time":138181,"text":"I was never subjected to religion\nthrough a cultural lens."},{"time":142895,"text":"I was treated the same,"},{"time":144961,"text":"the same was expected of me."},{"time":147740,"text":"I was never taught that God\njudged differently based on gender."},{"time":152647,"text":"And my parents' understanding of God\nas a merciful and beneficial friend"},{"time":158289,"text":"and provider shaped the way\nI looked at the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162143,"text":"Now, of course, my upbringing\nhad additional benefits."},{"time":166970,"text":"Being one of 11 children is Diplomacy 101.\n(Laughter)"},{"time":172592,"text":"To this day, I am asked\nwhere I went to school,"},{"time":175169,"text":"like, \"Did you go to\nKennedy School of Government?\""},{"time":177652,"text":"and I look at them and I'm like, \"No,"},{"time":179558,"text":"I went to the Murabit School\nof International Affairs.\""},{"time":182367,"text":"It's extremely exclusive. You would have\nto talk to my mom to get in."},{"time":188195,"text":"Lucky for you, she's here."},{"time":191879,"text":"But being one of 11 children\nand having 10 siblings"},{"time":196368,"text":"teaches you a lot about\npower structures and alliances."},{"time":200600,"text":"It teaches you focus; you have\nto talk fast or say less,"},{"time":203403,"text":"because you will always get cut off."},{"time":205911,"text":"It teaches you the importance\nof messaging."},{"time":208767,"text":"You have to ask questions in the right way\nto get the answers you know you want,"},{"time":212993,"text":"and you have to say no\nin the right way to keep the peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":217172,"text":"But the most important lesson\nI learned growing up"},{"time":221444,"text":"was the importance of being at the table."},{"time":224974,"text":"When my mom's favorite lamp broke,\nI had to be there when she was trying"},{"time":228805,"text":"to find out how and by who,\nbecause I had to defend myself,"},{"time":233334,"text":"because if you're not,\nthen the finger is pointed at you,"},{"time":237117,"text":"and before you know it,\nyou will be grounded."},{"time":239741,"text":"I am not speaking\nfrom experience, of course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244338,"text":"When I was 15 in 2005,\nI completed high school and I moved"},{"time":249750,"text":"from Canada -- Saskatoon --"},{"time":252240,"text":"to Zawiya, my parents' hometown in Libya,"},{"time":256319,"text":"a very traditional city."},{"time":258711,"text":"Mind you, I had only ever been\nto Libya before on vacation,"},{"time":263530,"text":"and as a seven-year-old girl,\nit was magic."},{"time":267906,"text":"It was ice cream and trips to the beach\nand really excited relatives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273468,"text":"Turns out it's not the same\nas a 15-year-old young lady."},{"time":278470,"text":"I very quickly became introduced\nto the cultural aspect of religion."},{"time":284438,"text":"The words \"haram\" --\nmeaning religiously prohibited --"},{"time":288896,"text":"and \"aib\" -- meaning\nculturally inappropriate --"},{"time":292402,"text":"were exchanged carelessly,"},{"time":295118,"text":"as if they meant the same thing\nand had the same consequences."},{"time":299437,"text":"And I found myself in conversation\nafter conversation with classmates"},{"time":304174,"text":"and colleagues, professors,\nfriends, even relatives,"},{"time":307610,"text":"beginning to question my own role\nand my own aspirations."},{"time":312393,"text":"And even with the foundation\nmy parents had provided for me,"},{"time":315923,"text":"I found myself questioning\nthe role of women in my faith."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320218,"text":"So at the Murabit School\nof International Affairs,"},{"time":324397,"text":"we go very heavy on the debate,"},{"time":327137,"text":"and rule number one is do your research,\nso that's what I did,"},{"time":332640,"text":"and it surprised me how easy it was"},{"time":336425,"text":"to find women in my faith\nwho were leaders,"},{"time":340442,"text":"who were innovative, who were strong --"},{"time":343994,"text":"politically, economically,\neven militarily."},{"time":347360,"text":"Khadija financed the Islamic movement"},{"time":350751,"text":"in its infancy."},{"time":352562,"text":"We wouldn't be here if it weren't for her."},{"time":355627,"text":"So why weren't we learning about her?"},{"time":358274,"text":"Why weren't we learning about these women?"},{"time":361195,"text":"Why were women being relegated\nto positions which predated"},{"time":363986,"text":"the teachings of our faith?"},{"time":366656,"text":"And why, if we are equal\nin the eyes of God,"},{"time":368931,"text":"are we not equal in the eyes of men?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":372623,"text":"To me, it all came back to the lessons\nI had learned as a child."},{"time":378350,"text":"The decision maker, the person\nwho gets to control the message,"},{"time":382022,"text":"is sitting at the table,"},{"time":384604,"text":"and unfortunately,\nin every single world faith,"},{"time":389504,"text":"they are not women."},{"time":392150,"text":"Religious institutions\nare dominated by men"},{"time":395192,"text":"and driven by male leadership,"},{"time":397143,"text":"and they create policies\nin their likeness,"},{"time":400579,"text":"and until we can change\nthe system entirely,"},{"time":404672,"text":"then we can't realistically\nexpect to have full economic"},{"time":407939,"text":"and political participation of women."},{"time":411515,"text":"Our foundation is broken."},{"time":415786,"text":"My mom actually says, you can't build\na straight house on a crooked foundation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":422521,"text":"In 2011, the Libyan revolution broke out,\nand my family was on the front lines."},{"time":429580,"text":"And there's this amazing thing\nthat happens in war,"},{"time":432644,"text":"a cultural shift almost, very temporary."},{"time":435773,"text":"And it was the first time that I felt\nit was not only acceptable"},{"time":438844,"text":"for me to be involved,\nbut it was encouraged."},{"time":441816,"text":"It was demanded."},{"time":444161,"text":"Myself and other women\nhad a seat at the table."},{"time":447170,"text":"We weren't holding hands or a medium."},{"time":450569,"text":"We were part of decision making."},{"time":452427,"text":"We were information sharing.\nWe were crucial."},{"time":455840,"text":"And I wanted and needed\nfor that change to be permanent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462342,"text":"Turns out, that's not that easy."},{"time":465128,"text":"It only took a few weeks before the women\nthat I had previously worked with"},{"time":469500,"text":"were returning back\nto their previous roles,"},{"time":472470,"text":"and most of them were driven\nby words of encouragement"},{"time":475275,"text":"from religious and political leaders,"},{"time":478177,"text":"most of whom cited religious scripture\nas their defense."},{"time":482449,"text":"It's how they gained popular support\nfor their opinions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487080,"text":"So initially, I focused on the economic\nand political empowerment of women."},{"time":492317,"text":"I thought that would lead\nto cultural and social change."},{"time":495823,"text":"It turns out, it does a little,\nbut not a lot."},{"time":500165,"text":"I decided to use\ntheir defense as my offense,"},{"time":504530,"text":"and I began to cite and highlight\nIslamic scripture as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509174,"text":"In 2012 and 2013, my organization\nled the single largest"},{"time":513736,"text":"and most widespread\ncampaign in Libya."},{"time":516221,"text":"We entered homes and schools\nand universities, even mosques."},{"time":520997,"text":"We spoke to 50,000 people directly,"},{"time":523279,"text":"and hundreds of thousands more through\nbillboards and television commercials,"},{"time":527343,"text":"radio commercials and posters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530130,"text":"And you're probably wondering how\na women's rights organization"},{"time":533194,"text":"was able to do this in communities\nwhich had previously opposed"},{"time":536166,"text":"our sheer existence."},{"time":539701,"text":"I used scripture."},{"time":542170,"text":"I used verses from the Quran\nand sayings of the Prophet,"},{"time":547560,"text":"Hadiths, his sayings which\nare, for example,"},{"time":551525,"text":"\"The best of you is the best\nto their family.\""},{"time":554961,"text":"\"Do not let your brother oppress another.\""},{"time":558978,"text":"For the first time, Friday sermons\nled by local community imams"},{"time":563993,"text":"promoted the rights of women."},{"time":566478,"text":"They discussed taboo issues,\nlike domestic violence."},{"time":570656,"text":"Policies were changed."},{"time":574080,"text":"In certain communities,\nwe actually had to go as far"},{"time":577205,"text":"as saying the International\nHuman Rights Declaration,"},{"time":581106,"text":"which you opposed because it wasn't\nwritten by religious scholars,"},{"time":585192,"text":"well, those same principles\nare in our book."},{"time":589975,"text":"So really, the United Nations\njust copied us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":595931,"text":"By changing the message,\nwe were able to provide"},{"time":598774,"text":"an alternative narrative which promoted\nthe rights of women in Libya."},{"time":603349,"text":"It's something that has now\nbeen replicated internationally,"},{"time":608201,"text":"and while I am not saying it's easy --\nbelieve me, it's not."},{"time":612590,"text":"Liberals will say you're using religion\nand call you a bad conservative."},{"time":616421,"text":"Conservatives will call you\na lot of colorful things."},{"time":619904,"text":"I've heard everything from, \"Your parents\nmust be extremely ashamed of you\" --"},{"time":623990,"text":"false; they're my biggest fans --"},{"time":626100,"text":"to \"You will not make it\nto your next birthday\" --"},{"time":628611,"text":"again wrong, because I did."},{"time":632674,"text":"And I remain"},{"time":634810,"text":"a very strong believer that women's rights\nand religion are not mutually exclusive."},{"time":642291,"text":"But we have to be at the table."},{"time":645723,"text":"We have to stop giving up our position,\nbecause by remaining silent,"},{"time":649856,"text":"we allow for the continued persecution\nand abuse of women worldwide."},{"time":655837,"text":"By saying that we're going\nto fight for women's rights"},{"time":658842,"text":"and fight extremism\nwith bombs and warfare,"},{"time":662627,"text":"we completely cripple local societies\nwhich need to address these issues"},{"time":666876,"text":"so that they're sustainable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671496,"text":"It is not easy, challenging\ndistorted religious messaging."},{"time":676930,"text":"You will have your fair share\nof insults and ridicule and threats."},{"time":682380,"text":"But we have to do it."},{"time":684216,"text":"We have no other option than to reclaim\nthe message of human rights,"},{"time":688957,"text":"the principles of our faith,"},{"time":691604,"text":"not for us, not for\nthe women in your families,"},{"time":694367,"text":"not for the women in this room,"},{"time":696317,"text":"not even for the women out there,"},{"time":699491,"text":"but for societies\nthat would be transformed"},{"time":702997,"text":"with the participation of women."},{"time":705884,"text":"And the only way we can do that,"},{"time":708391,"text":"our only option,"},{"time":710179,"text":"is to be, and remain, at the table."}]},{"cues":[{"time":713709,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":716332,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}